 anthropology. Coming at a time when some question the viability of the discipline, the message of this powerful and original work is especially welcome, as it not only promotes a new way of doing anthropology, but also compellingly articulates a new rationale for why anthropology matters.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aIndigenous peoplesxLand tenurezPapua New Guinea. 0aIndigenous peoplesxLegal status, laws, etczPapua New Guinea. 0aIndigenous peoplesxLegal status, laws, etc.zPapua New Guinea. 0aMineral industriesxEnvironmental aspectszPapua New Guinea. 0aPublic anthropologyzPapua New Guinea. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311066767740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780520970090?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520970090423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520970090/original  a978-3-11-066767-7  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles